Name:           python-parse
Version:        1.20.1
Release:        0
Summary:        Python module for parsing strings using a "format" syntax
License:        MIT
URL:            https://github.com/r1chardj0n3s/parse
Source0:        https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/source/p/parse/parse-%{version}.tar.gz
